Web Server Resources
====================

This folder contains resources for the Web Server application.

Templates File
--------------
You need to create a Templates file (filetype &FEC) containing a "proginfo"
window template. Use WinEd, TemplEd, or FormEd on RISC OS to create it.

The "proginfo" window should contain:
- Icon 0: Application name (e.g., "Web Server")  
- Icon 1: Purpose (e.g., "HTTP server for Converse BBS")
- Icon 2: Author (e.g., "Converse BBS")
- Icon 3: Version (e.g., "1.00 (28 Nov 2025)")

Alternatively, copy an existing proginfo template from another Converse
application (Server, FTN, etc.) and modify it.

Sprites File
------------
Create an !Sprites file (filetype &FF9) containing:
- !web: Application icon for the iconbar (small, 34x17 or similar)
- Optionally: sm!web (small icon for icon bar)

Use Paint or another sprite editor on RISC OS to create these.
